                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/179.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consul
                            <persName type="to">Letcher</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-02-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 25, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In compliance with a request from the Spanish Embassy, renew your efforts to have
                    an investigation of the killing of the Gonzalez brothers. Impress with all
                    earnestness upon appropriate authorities the extreme importance of having this
                    action taken immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
